channel.title: How do I remove this from the quest tab?
channel.description:
They're links, but you can't click them, or if you do click them they do nothing. I've looked through the entire client folder and source folder and can't find out how to change this! I also showed in the picture what it shows when you right click it.
[URL=http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/707/unledttw.png/][IMG]http://img707.imageshack.us/img707/4673/unledttw.png[/img][/URL]
And also right below it where it says the website, how do I change that too?

item.title: How do I remove this from the quest tab?
item.dc:creator: @escalation escalation
item.description:
@escalation wrote:

It is in then Client files > RSinterfaces.java > search for what your looking for…

If it’s server sided go to Server files > Client.java or Clickingbuttons.java > Search for what your looking for…
